<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xml:lang="en"><generator uri="https://gohugo.io/" version="0.85.0">Hugo</generator><title type="html">footloose on ilo</title><link href="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/tags/footloose/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="HTML"/><link href="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/tags/footloose/index.xml" rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" title="RSS"/><link href="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/tags/footloose/atom.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" title="Atom"/><updated>2021-07-12T04:56:11+00:00</updated><id>https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/tags/footloose/</id><entry><title type="html">Runtimes</title><link href="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/compose/runtimes/?utm_source=atom_feed" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><link href="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/shell/runtimes/?utm_source=atom_feed" rel="related" type="text/html" title="Runtimes"/><id>https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/compose/runtimes/</id><published>2020-04-13T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2020-04-13T00:00:00+00:00</updated><content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><code>ilo compose</code> by default searches your local system for supported runtimes. It prefers <code>docker-compose</code> over <code>podman-compose</code> over <code>pods-compose</code> over <code>footloose</code> over <code>vagrant</code> at the moment. In order to force the usage of a specific runtime, use the <code>--runtime</code> flag.</p>
<h2 id="docker-compose">docker-compose</h2>
<p>Force <code>ilo</code> to use <a href="https://docs.docker.com/compose/">docker-compose</a> like this:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="chroma"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">$ ilo shell --runtime docker-compose

<span class="c1"># alias</span>
$ ilo shell --runtime dc
</code></pre></div><h2 id="podman-compose">podman-compose</h2>
<p>Force <code>ilo</code> to use <a href="https://github.com/containers/podman-compose">podman-compose</a> like this:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre class="chroma"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">$ ilo shell --runtime podman-copose

<span class="c1"># alias</span>
$ ilo shell --runtime pc
</code></pre></div>]]></content><category scheme="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/categories/compose" term="compose" label="compose"/><category scheme="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/tags/runtime" term="runtime" label="runtime"/><category scheme="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/tags/docker-compose" term="docker-compose" label="docker-compose"/><category scheme="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/tags/footloose" term="footloose" label="footloose"/><category scheme="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/tags/podman-compose" term="podman-compose" label="podman-compose"/><category scheme="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/tags/pods-compose" term="pods-compose" label="pods-compose"/><category scheme="https://ilo.projects.metio.wtf/tags/vagrant" term="vagrant" label="vagrant"/></entry></feed>